<li><strong>First-page Google results average 1,447 words.</strong> Ranking in position #1 correlates with 2,200+ words.</li>
<li><strong>Long-form content earns 77% more backlinks</strong> and 56% more social shares than short content.</li>
<li><strong>94% of blog posts earn zero backlinks.</strong> Length alone does not guarantee links. Quality and originality matter more.</li>
