<li><strong>Only 9% of bloggers write 2,000+ words.</strong> The opportunity is in the gap between what most people write and what actually performs.</li>
<li><strong>AI reduced average writing time</strong> from 4+ hours to 3.5 hours. 80% of bloggers now use AI.</li>
</ul>
